## Cost of Running the System

This section provides an estimated monthly cost for deploying and running the ICSJ Grave Management System in a production environment. Actual costs may vary depending on usage, scale, and infrastructure choices.

---

### 1. Hosting (Frontend)

- Platform: Vercel / Netlify  
- Estimated Cost: Free – $20/month  

---

### 2. Backend & Database (Supabase)

- Services:
  - PostgreSQL Database  
  - Authentication  
  - APIs  
- Estimated Cost: $25/month (Pro Plan)  

---

### 3. Automation (n8n)

- Option 1: Self-hosted (recommended)
  - Hosting (VPS): $5 – $10/month  
- Option 2: n8n Cloud
  - Cost: $20+/month  

---

### 4. Email Service

- Services: SMTP / SendGrid / Resend  
- Estimated Cost: Free – $15/month (depending on email volume)  

---

### 5. Domain & DNS

- Domain name: $10 – $15/year  
- DNS (Cloudflare): Free  

---

### 6. AI Chatbot (Optional Cost)

- If using OpenAI / external API:
  - Estimated Cost: $5 – $20/month (based on usage)  
- If using local/static assistant:
  - Cost: Minimal / Free  

---

### Estimated Total Monthly Cost

| Setup Type        | Estimated Cost |
|------------------|---------------|
| Minimum Setup    | $10 – $20     |
| Standard Setup   | $30 – $60     |
| Scaled Setup     | $60 – $120    |

---

### Notes

- Costs increase with:
  - Number of users  
  - Database size  
  - Email volume  
  - AI usage  

- Self-hosting automation (n8n) significantly reduces cost.

---

### Cost Optimization Strategies

- Use free tiers for early deployment  
- Self-host n8n workflows  
- Optimize database queries  
- Limit unnecessary API calls  
- Use caching where possible  

---

## Summary

The ICSJ Grave Management System is designed to be cost-efficient and scalable. A fully functional production system can be deployed at a relatively low monthly cost, making it suitable for small to large Islamic centers.
